r34761 | dph | 2016-08-05 08:13:18 -0700 (Fri, 05 Aug 2016) | 2 lines

Removed the is_a relation between 'cellular develo0pmental process' and 'developmental process' that I added yesterday. It turns out that it was not necessary because 'cellular developmental process' was already a single-organism developmental process.
